<div class="title">I Really Enjoyed my Trip!</div>
<div class="substance">2C-I</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Viaticus&Exact=1">Viaticus</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Viaticus. "I Really Enjoyed my Trip!: An Experience with 2C-I (exp44489)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 19, 2008. erowid.org/exp/44489</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

